{"title":"Näomaskid ja koorijad","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"norrskin-night-repair-face-mask-50ml","title":"NorrSkin Night Repair Face Mask 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eMoisturises, soothes and repairs your skin, supports the renewal of the epidermis. Rich in vitamins and minerals, non-comedogenic.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBenefits: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRepairs damaged and tired skin while bringing back natural healthy look\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBalance oil\/sebum production with Niacinamide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt softens skin texture with Jojoba Oil and Linseed oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMineralise and boost your skin with vitamins\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt smoothes skin and prevents irritations\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeeply nourishes and repairs skin immune barrier with the power of Niacinamide and Linseed extract\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt reduces appearance of fine lines and wrinkles\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e When used daily it has strong anti-aging benefits\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eSqualane\u003c\/span\u003e protects the skin from water loss. Deeply moisturises the skin, has a mild formula, making it suitable for sensitive skin, regulates production of sebum, has a strong anti-aging effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eLinseed Oil\u003c\/span\u003e is extra-rich, plant-derived source of Omega-3 fatty acids. Provides a nourishing lipid barrier.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera Gel\u003c\/span\u003e is soothing, anti-bacterial, anti-fungal, cleansing and moisturising.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e97,5% natural origin ingredients, dermatologically tested.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a generous amount of the mask on clean skin. Leave for 10-15 minutes. Massage remaining part into the skin. Use regularly 1-2 times a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Oil, Squalane, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Glyceryl Stearate, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, 1,2-Hexanediol, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil, Hamamelis Virginiana Water, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Extract, Fragaria Vesca Fruit Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Pantolactone, Panthenol, Xanthan Gum, Parfum, Lactic Acid, Sodium Phytate, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Hydroxyacetophenone, Linalool, Citronellol, Hexyl Cinnamal. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNatural Certified | Clean Certified | Vegan Certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eInspired by Hälsingland, Sweden.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNorrSkin plants 1 tree for every product sold.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"bioskina","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49308422603079,"sku":null,"price":36.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/norrskin-night-repair-face-mask-50ml-403415.png?v=1739897341"},{"product_id":"hej-naked-pink-exfoliating-mask-30ml","title":"HEJ Organic Naked Pink Exfoliating Mask 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaked is a fragrance-free skincare line with highly effective and 100% natural ingredients.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePink exfoliating formula combines triple care for your skin: exfoliation, moisture and protection.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAHA acids\u003c\/span\u003e work in the upper layers of your skin, removing dead skin cells and dirt.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBHA acids\u003c\/span\u003e can penetrate deeper, both together are known for an effective peeling result.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFive-fold moisture complex\u003c\/span\u003e made of glycerin, pentylene glycol, betaine, hyaluronic acid and biosaccharide gum can prevent signs of dehydration and leaves the skin feeling fresh.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTriple skin care: exfoliation, hydration and protection\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEffective AHA and BHA chemical peel for instantly softening skin and strengthening the barrier\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFive-fold moisture complex to combat signs of dehydration\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSkin type: Particularly suitable for impure, oily and combination skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% fragrance-free and natural\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply once a week to your cleansed facial skin, avoiding the eye area. Leave it on for 5 minutes and rinse completely with warm water. Use sunscreen in the first 24 hours after application. When using acid peels for the first time, reduce the application time (2-3 minutes) and increase it continuously. If skin irritation occurs, discontinue use immediately. Not for irritated or sensitive skin, do not use on wounds and open areas. Keep out of reach of children.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Pentylene Glycol, Betaine, Glycerin, Zea Mays Starch, Salicylic Acid, Xanthan Gum, Pectin, Bisabolol, Dipotassium Glycyrrhizate, Sodium Hydroxide, Citric Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Lactic Acid, Mica, Chondrus Crispus Powder, Sodium Hyaluronate, CI 77891, Tartaric Acid, CI 77491, Tocopherol, Glucose, Biosaccharide Gum-1, Acer Saccharum Extract, Sodium Levulinate, Silica, Glyceryl Caprylate, Sodium Anisate, Tin Oxide, Citrus Limon Peel Oil *ingredients from certified organic agriculture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49515612078407,"sku":null,"price":15.4,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-naked-pink-exfoliating-mask-30ml-398506.png?v=1739897243"},{"product_id":"hej-naked-enzyme-peeling-powder-30g","title":"HEJ Organic Naked Enzyme Peeling Powder 30g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan class=\"TextRun SCXW187668887 BCX4\" lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"none\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187668887 BCX4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaked is a fragrance-free skincare line with highly effective and 100% natural ingredients.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan class=\"TextRun SCXW187668887 BCX4\" lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"none\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187668887 BCX4\"\u003eThe\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"TextRun SCXW187668887 BCX4\" lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"none\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187668887 BCX4\"\u003eNaked Enzyme Peeling Powder\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"TextRun SCXW187668887 BCX4\" lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"none\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187668887 BCX4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003egently but effectively removes dead skin cells and gives you a long-term smooth and soft skin feeling. Zinc and azelaic acid help prevent impurities. Moreover, organic apricot kernel\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2 SCXW187668887 BCX4\"\u003epeeling\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187668887 BCX4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eand organic jojoba oil are particularly gentle to your skin and leave an even complexion and a smooth skin feeling.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSkin type: blemished, oily, and combination skin    \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eContains zinc and azelaic acid to combat impurities\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh appearance and a smooth skin feeling\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGentle peeling for an even complexion\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e100 % fragrance-free and natural\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan class=\"TextRun SCXW49320398 BCX4\" lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"none\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW49320398 BCX4\"\u003eOnce or twice a week, put a hazelnut-sized amount into your moistened hands and lather on your skin. Use circular motions to spread over your face for 1-2 minutes and then rinse off with water. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e Apply sunscreen during the day. Keep out of reach of children.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Talc, Maltodextrin, Magnesium Sulfate, Prunus Armeniaca Seed Powder*, Betaine, Aqua, Azelaic Acid, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil*, Prunus Armeniaca Fruit Extract*, Lipase, Protease, Zinc Pca, Bisabolol, Glycerin, Xanthan Gum * from certified organic agriculture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49515844239687,"sku":null,"price":17.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-naked-enzyme-peeling-powder-30g-875333.png?v=1739897244"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-facial-scrub-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Facial Scrub 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGentle organic facial scrub to effectively cleanse and remove dead skin cells, leaving the skin soft and refreshed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade with o\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003erganic whey (nourishing), finely ground apricot kernels (exfoliating), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic wheat germ oil (nurturing) and organic extracts of camomile (antiseptic), rose hip (anti-inflammatory) and marigold (regenerating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage gently into dry and clean skin. Moisten fingertips with warm water and massage again till the scrub turns into a white creamy texture. Rinse off with lukewarm water. Use 1-2 times per week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Glycerin**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Prunus Armeniaca Seed Powder**, Aqua*, Xanthan Gum*, Kaolin*, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Anisate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Rosa Canina Fruit Extract**, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (92,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901084832071,"sku":null,"price":37.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-facial-scrub-50ml-749873.jpg?v=1739897173"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-facial-masque-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Facial Masque 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePurifying organic mask to gently yet effectively cleanse, soothe and hydrate the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade with organic whey (nourishing), white clay (purifying), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic witch hazel water (nurturing), organic rosehip seed oil (soothing), and organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), cucumber (refreshing) and mallow (protecting).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a generous layer to clean face and neck. Leave for 15 minutes until dry. Rinse gently with warm water. Use once or twice a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Hamamelis Virginiana Water**, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Glycerin**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Aqua*, Kaolin*, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Oenothera Biennis Oil**, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Potassium Sorbate, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Cucumis Sativus Fruit Extract**, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**, Sodium Lactate*.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (81,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901095088455,"sku":null,"price":40.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-facial-masque-50ml-901935.jpg?v=1739897176"},{"product_id":"naif-circular-face-scrub-50ml","title":"NAIF Circular Face Scrub 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaïf Circular Face Scrub cleanses your skin and removes dead skin cells, stimulating cell renewal. Result: radiant skin. The face scrub also contains natural oils, such as macadamia, avocado and sweet almond oil. These ingredients condition your skin and keep your skin soft and supple, without making your face feel tight, after exfoliating. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Naïf products are 100% vegan, made with a gentle fragrance and are dermatologically tested, free from the 26 most common allergens. Mild for the skin, due to the fine grain, which also allows you to use the scrub several times a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eScrub your face once or twice a week for beautiful, healthy skin. Slightly moisten your face and apply the pea-sized scrub to the inside of your hand. Using your fingers, massage the scrub onto your face for at least 30 seconds using circular motions. Rinse with lukewarm water. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Calcium Carbonate, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil, Persea Gratissima Oil, Methylpropanediol, Cetyl Alcohol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Sucrose Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Linum Usitatissimum Oil, Caprylyl Glycol, Parfum, Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Phenylpropanol, Bisabolol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915785441607,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-circular-face-scrub-50ml-570470.png?v=1739897161"},{"product_id":"madara-peel-brightening-aha-peel-mask-60ml","title":"MÁDARA PEEL Brightening AHA Peel mask 60ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eGive your skin an instant radiance boost with this active AHA peeling mask. Formulated with nature’s superdose of active acids, this mask ensures multiple skincare benefits: Removes the dead cells to uncover smoother, more radiant skin surface, exfoliates to stimulate cell turnover and regeneration, brightens the complexion and diminishes appearance of age-spots and fine lines, helps to unclog pores and improves the absorption and effect of other cosmetic products. Especially beneficial for dull, tired skin with signs of aging, lines, wrinkles, age-spots, lack of glow, clogged pores and acne.\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e ​Apply to clean skin, leave on for 3–10 minutes. Rinse off thoroughly, follow with a toner and moisturiser of your choice.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Lactic Acid, Glycerin, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Flower Water, Galactoarabinan, Potassium Hydroxide, Microcrystalline Cellulose, Glucomannan, Mica (CI 77019), CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Aroma, Cellulose gum, Pyrus Cydonia (Quince) Fruit Extract, Sambucus Nigra (Elder) Flower Extract, Ethyl Lauroyl Arginate HCl, Xanthan Gum, Benzyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916404298055,"sku":"","price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-peel-brightening-aha-peel-mask-60ml-412418.jpg?v=1739897193"},{"product_id":"madara-detox-ultra-purifying-mud-mask-60ml","title":"MÁDARA DETOX Ultra Purifying MUD mask 60ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eClarify, rejuvenate and recharge the skin with this deep-purifying detox mask. Formulated with Nordic forest lake mud, this mask ensures multiple skincare benefits: it purifies the complexion, tightens pores and conditions, absorbs excess oils, reduces outbreaks, detoxifies the skin, eliminates traces of acne and minor inflammation and helps to retain skin’s hydration. Leaves the skin feeling clean, fresh, revitalized.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e \u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;\"\u003e​\u003c\/span\u003eRecommended to use twice a week as clarifying treatment for oily, combination skin, skin with enlarged pores, blemishes, acne. Once a week to combat skin dullness, tiredness and occasional inflammation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Kaolin, Glycerin, Montmorillonite, Diatomaceous Earth, Butylene Glycol, Aqua, Sodium PCA, Sodium levulinate, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Tocopherol, Xanthan Gum, Propanediol, Lactic Acid, Sodium anisate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Charcoal Powder, Alchemilla Vulgaris (Lady's Mantle) Extract, Algae (Algae) Extract, Nasturtium Officinale (Watercress) Flower\/Leaf Extract, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), CI 75810 (Chlorophyll), Rhamnose, Maltodextrin, Glucose, Glucuronic Acid\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**Pure mineral pigments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e16% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916409999687,"sku":"","price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-detox-ultra-purifying-mud-mask-60ml-293845.jpg?v=1739897183"},{"product_id":"madara-peel-creamy-clay-aha-peel-mask-60ml","title":"MÁDARA PEEL Creamy Clay AHA Peel Mask 60ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003eUniting 7% lactic acid and micro-clay, this supercharged face mask works to gently polish the skin’s surface, sloughing off dead skin cells and unclogging pores to reveal a clearer, fresher and more radiant complexion.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003eThe dermatologically tested formula encourages a more even skin tone and improves texture, contributing to softer, smoother and brighter skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003eEnriched with white clay which binds impurities and helps prevent breakouts, as well as jojoba oil and extract of yarrow that boast soothing and anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003eNot suitable for fragile, hypersensitive skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal;\"\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Gently massage over clean face and neck in circular motions, avoiding the eye area. Leave on for 3-10 minutes. Follow with a moisturiser of your choice. Use 2-3 times weekly, avoid sun exposure after use. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Kaolin, Lactic Acid, Glycerin, Pentylene Glycol, Polyglyceryl-6 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Potassium Hydroxide, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Xanthan Gum, Polyglyceryl-6 Behenate, Aroma, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Palmitic acid, Perlite, Stearic Acid, Achillea Millefolium (Yarrow) Extract, Charcoal Powder, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Tocopherol, Linalool, Geraniol, Citral, Limonene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916412555591,"sku":"","price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-peel-creamy-clay-aha-peel-mask-60ml-458560.jpg?v=1739897164"},{"product_id":"madara-sos-hydra-instant-moisture-radiance-mask-60ml","title":"MÁDARA SOS HYDRA Instant Moisture + Radiance mask 60ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis intense nourishing face mask provides an immediate comfort for tight, stressed and dehydrated skin. The formula with a blend of moisturizing natural sugars, Northern peony, hyaluronic acid, linseed and nettle deeply hydrates and improves the look and feel of the skin, providing instant and persistent results. This rich texture mask pampers the skin, reduces signs of fatigue, conditions, tones, smooths and protects the skin from environmental damage and premature ageing.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Use twice a week or whenever the skin feels tight, dehydrated and stressed. Apply to clean skin. Leave it on or wipe off with a cotton pad or a cloth after 15–20 minutes. To reinforce mask’s moisturising benefits and ensure long-term results, follow with MÁDARA SOS Hydra Repair Intensive Serum and\/or SOS Hydra Recharge Cream.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Water, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Arachidyl Alcohol, Behenyl Alcohol, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Extract, Sodium PCA, Sodium levulinate, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Arachidyl Glucoside, Aqua, Aroma, Betaine, Sodium anisate, Coco-glucoside, Lactic Acid, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Seed Extract, Paeonia Lactiflora (Peony) Root Extract, Urtica Dioica (Nettle) Leaf Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Xanthan Gum, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Hydrolyzed Glycosaminoglycans, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Sodium phytate, Tocopherol, Xylitylglucoside, Anhydroxylitol, Benzyl Alcohol, Xylitol, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol, Geraniol, Benzyl Salicylate, Eugenol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916422222151,"sku":"","price":32.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-hydra-instant-moisture-radiance-mask-60ml-706318.jpg?v=1739897177"},{"product_id":"clarification-the-radiance-exfoliating-face-scrub-60g","title":"Clarification The Radiance Exfoliating Face Scrub 60g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis brand believes in a future where beauty coexists harmoniously with sustainability.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% purity treatments, 0% added water!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Radiance Powder ensures a very gentle exfoliation for the face. The skin regains its natural radiance. 100% ingredients of natural origin formula with rice powder and chamomile flower extracts.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Mix this exfoliating powder in your wet hand, apply on wet skin and massage in circular movements. Rinse thoroughly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDo not inhale or breathe the dust, avoid contact with eyes. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003ePUMICE, ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) POWDER, CELLULOSE, CHAMOMILLA RECUTITA (MATRICARIA) FLOWER\/LEAF EXTRACT, SACCHARUM OFFICINARUM (SUGAR CANE) EXTRACT, KAOLIN, PRUNUS ARMENIACA (APRICOT) SEED POWDER, PARFUM (FRAGRANCE).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% of natural origin ingredients  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Clarification","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50965011530055,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/clarification-the-radiance-exfoliating-face-scrub-60g-543656.jpg?v=1739897187"},{"product_id":"berrichi-reveal-purity-powder-scrub-12g","title":"BERRICHI Reveal Purity Powder Scrub 12g","description":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover the Berrich Powder scrub – a gentle and effective exfoliator that removes dirt and brings skin back to life. The ingredients in this unique exfoliator combine natural powers and scientific precision to leave your skin silky soft and fresh.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGently removes dirt and dead skin cells\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSupports skin renewal and elasticity\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoothes inflammation and reduces uneven skin tone\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLeaves skin smooth and matte, without a tugging sensation\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eContains powerful natural antioxidants that help protect the skin from free radicals.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFurcellaran\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eJojoba pearls\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e –\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003eensure effective but gentle exfoliation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBamboo Flour\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e –\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eeffectively absorbs excess oil, leaving oily and combination skin feeling soft and smooth. It has antibacterial properties and helps fight acne. Promotes healing of inflammations, calms and regulates sebaceous glands.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAlgalite\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e–\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003ethis algae powder helps to gently exfoliate the skin without causing micro-injuries, helps to balance the activity of the sebaceous glands.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eSprinkle a small amount of exfoliator on the palm of your hand, add a few drops of water and rub until you get a light lather. Apply the mixture to the skin and massage in gentle circular motions. Rinse thoroughly with warm water. For dry skin, use 1x a week and avoid cheeks. For normal and oily skin, it can be used up to 2x a week.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eBambusa Arundinacea Stem Extract (kooriva toimega Bambusejahu), Oryza Sativa Starch (Riisitärklis), Sodium Lauroyl Glutamate (vahtu tekitav aine), Cellulose (Koorivad oraanžid pärlikesed), Lithothamnion Calcareum Powder (Algalite vetikas) , Hydrogenated Jojoba Oil (Koorivad valged pärlikesed), Furcellaria Lumbricalis Extract (Vetikas), CI 77492, CI 77491.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084218696007,"sku":null,"price":21.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-reveal-purity-powder-scrub-12g-697773.png?v=1739979951"},{"product_id":"hoia-fruit-acid-face-mask-fruitfest-50ml","title":"HOIA Fruit Acid Face Mask Fruitfest 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe mask containing fruit acids (AHA) and natural salicylic acid (BHA) helps to exfoliate dead skin cells, while simultaneously stimulating the production of new skin cells and collagen in the skin. The mask helps moisturize the skin, prevent the formation of pigmentation spots, alleviate acne, smooth out superficial wrinkles, make the skin more elastic and give the complexion a fresh and radiant appearance.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Cleanse the skin of makeup residues and apply a suitable amount to damp skin, avoiding the eye and lip areas, and leave the mask on for 5-10 minutes. Then rinse thoroughly with warm water and apply serum, oil or cream to the skin. Use 1-2 times a week. Discontinue use if rash, itching, or burning occurs during use. Mild tingling on the face is natural.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHowever, it is important to use AHA acids cautiously, especially on sensitive skin, and apply sunscreen to the skin if necessary, as acids can make the skin more sensitive to UV rays.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Rosa Damascena Distillate, *Citrus Aurantium Flower Distillate, Sargassum Fluitans Extract, *Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, *Simmondsia Chinensis oil, Salix Nigra extract, Saccharum Officinarum Extract, Vaccinium Myrtillus Extract, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Extract, Acer Saccharum Extract, Citrus Medica Limonum Extract, Xanthan Gum, Pentylene Glycol, Water, Hibiscus Sabdariffa Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Hydrolized Sodium Hyaluronate, Lactobacillus Ferment, Kaolin. *Organic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104830095687,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-fruit-acid-face-mask-fruitfest-50ml-877573.jpg?v=1740808668"},{"product_id":"upcircle-beauty-face-scrub-with-coffee-and-chamomile-floral-blend-100ml","title":"UpCircle Beauty Face Scrub with Coffee and Chamomile - Floral Blend 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eCoffee face scrub formulated for sensitive skin with chamomile, rosehip, geranium and patchouli essential oils.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRenowned for its anti-inflammatory properties, chamomile soothes redness and irritation, making an ideal remedy for skin complaints like rosacea, acne and psoriasis. Rich in vitamins E and B, jojoba oil deeply moisturises, helping dry, dehydrated skin regain hydration.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis organic face scrub gently buffs away dry, dead cells to leave you feeling soft, smooth and glowy. Blended with shea butter to nourish the skin post-scrub.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eDampen your face with water and apply scrub in gentle circular motions. Leave it on for a few moments, then rinse with warm water and par dry. May be used 2-3 times a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Coffea Arabica Seed Powder, Sucrose, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Fruit Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil, Rosa Canina (Rosehip) Fruit Oil, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Peel Oil, Pelargonium Graveolens (Geranium) Flower Oil, Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary) Leaf Oil, Citrus Aurantium Bergamia (Bergamot) Fruit Oil, Pogostemom Cablin (Patchouli) Leaf Oil, Citrus Aurantium Amara (Bitter Orange) Leaf Oil, Anthemis Nobilis (Chamomile) Flower Oil, Benzyl Alcohol, Dehydroacetic Acid, Benzoic Acid, Sorbic Acid, *Limonene, *Citronellol, *Geraniol, *Linalool. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Natural constituent of essential oils listed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e99% NATURAL INGREDIENTS\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHandmade | Social Good | Recycled Materials | Zero Waste | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources | Non Toxic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"UpCircle Beauty","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51132666020167,"sku":null,"price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/upcircle-beauty-face-scrub-with-coffee-and-chamomile-floral-blend-100ml-904418.png?v=1740808673"},{"product_id":"upcircle-beauty-face-mask-with-kaolin-clay-60ml","title":"UpCircle Beauty Face Mask with Kaolin Clay 60ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eAn award-winning gently-detoxifying clay face mask to fight blackheads, minimise pores and prevent breakouts. Skin is left feeling cleansed, refreshed and balanced.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis clarifying kaolin clay face mask is suitable for all skin types. The olive powder is combined with rejuvenating white kaolin clay, coconut powder and baobab oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspiring, upcycling, uplifting: This detoxifying face mask is made with the finely-ground powder of discarded olive stones, a natural by-product of the olive oil industry and a powerful anti-inflammatory.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWinner of the CEW Responsibility Award 2022, winner in the Beauty Shortlist Awards 2021 and finalist in the Vogue Beauty Awards 2020.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to damp skin in a thin layer and relax for ten minutes. Rinse with warm water or a damp cloth to reveal fresh, cleansed skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Kaolin, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Milk Powder, Olea Europaea (Olive) Leaf Powder*, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter*, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Butter*, Glyceryl Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Adansonia Digitata (Baobab) Seed Oil, Curcuma Longa (Turmeric) Root Oil, Citrus Limonum (Lemon) Peel Oil, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Oil, Olea Europaea Fruit Oil, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract*, Cistus Ladaniferus Leaf Oil, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Oil, Zingiber Cassumunar (Plai) Root Oil, Cedrus Atlantica (Cedarwood) Bark Oil, Tocopherol, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Stearoyl Glutamate, Sucrose Stearate, Coco Glucoside, Coconut Alcohol, Dehydroacetic Acid, Lactic Acid, Benzyl Alcohol, Limonene**, Citral**, Linalool**, Geraniol**. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organically-grown ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Natural constituent of essential oils listed\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e99% NATURAL INGREDIENTS\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHandmade | Social Good | Recycled Materials | Zero Waste | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources | Non Toxic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"UpCircle Beauty","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51132854501703,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/upcircle-beauty-face-mask-with-kaolin-clay-60ml-860452.png?v=1740808673"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/masks.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}